@startuml
[*] --> Idle
Idle --> ChangingTime : press button
ChangingTime --> ChangingHour : change hour
ChangingHour --> ChangingMinute : press button
ChangingMinute --> ChangingAlarmHour : press button
ChangingAlarmHour --> ChangingAlarmMinute : press button
ChangingAlarmMinute --> Idle : press button
Idle --> AlarmOnOff : press button
AlarmOnOff --> AlarmOn : turn on alarm
AlarmOn --> Idle : current time matches set alarm, ring alarm
AlarmOn --> Idle : press stop button
Idle --> LightOnOff : press button
LightOnOff --> LightOn : turn light on
LightOn --> Idle : release button
@enduml
